description: Details of all reserved matters (Access, Appearance, Landscaping, Layout and Scale) pursuant to outline planning permission ref PA/13/02966 dated 24/12/2014 relating to the following areas of the Wood Wharf Masterplan:  i. Development Plot G3;  ii. Ground and above ground infrastructure, streets, landscaping and public realm within Development Zone G;  iii. Below ground floorspace and infrastructure for Development Plot G3; and  iv. Ground and above ground infrastructure, streets, landscaping and public realm outside Development Zone G but linked to i, ii and iii above.   Comprising 176 residential units (Use Class C3), 620sqm of flexible retail, office, leisure and/or community uses (Use Class A1-A5, B1, D1 and D2), ancillary space for circulation and residential facilities; as well as associated infrastructure, streets, landscaping, public realm, parking, servicing and utilities and other associated works.
